🔴 Problem
Finding reliable local service providers like plumbers, electricians, or tutors is often difficult, time-consuming, and lacks trust. Existing platforms are not truly hyperlocal and may involve high costs or delays.

🟢 Solution
NearAssist is a hyperlocal service marketplace that connects users with nearby service providers instantly. It enables quick discovery, booking, and interaction with trusted professionals within their locality.

⭐ Key Features
📍 Hyperlocal service matching
⚡ Instant booking system
🔐 Verified service providers
💰 Transparent pricing
📱 Simple and user-friendly interface

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: FireBase
Backend: VS Code
Hosting: Vercel

🌍 Impact
.Empowers local workers by increasing visibility and job opportunities
.Saves time for users by providing quick and reliable services
.Strengthens the local economy through digital connectivity
